item.title: CVE-2023-0891|2024-08-02T05:24:34.704Z -- unknown -- stagtools
item.description: The StagTools WordPress plugin before 2.3.7 does not validate and escape some of its shortcode attributes before outputting them back in a page/post where the shortcode is embed, which could allow users with the contributor role and above to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks.
